HEADWORD: Empiristic
<hw>Em`pi*ris"tic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Physics)</fld>
<def>Relating to, or resulting from, experience, or experiment;
following from empirical methods or data; -- opposed to
<contr>nativistic</contr>.</def>⟦br⟧
